<s> I defined a HTML application as dynamic HTML.  </s>
<s> Presents user interface, responds to user input and possibly reformats itself based on such.  </s>
<s> HTML applications are quite common place at Microsoft now.  </s>
<s> The Personal Web Server for Windows 95 and Windows 98 has had HTML based administration for 2 years, as does it's bigger brother, Internet Information Server.  </s>
<s> Outlook 98 has HTML based UI in several places - the Find and Organize features.  </s>
