<s> I think that it's important that the guidelines strongly address dynamic (small 'd') HTML with a refresher on Accessible Software Design - keyboard access, color, etc. Charles Oppermann Program Manager, Accessibility and Disabilities Group, Microsoft Corporation "A computer on every desk and in every home, usable by everyone!"  </s>
<s> What is an HTML application ?  </s>
<s> A DHTML page ?  </s>
